description: The Lono Ono Shave Ice truck brings refreshing Hawaiian style shave ice to Belleair, FL. Lono Ono means " Crazy Delicious" in Hawaiian and that is exactly what they are all about.  It all starts out with a scoop of vanilla bean ice cream mixed with fine shaven fluffy ice, topped off with homemade syrups, endless possibilities of the freshest fruits can be sure to refresh your taste buds. Last, serve in environment corn-based bio-degradable flower cups that will be sure to keep the sunshine state beautiful. All inspired by a tripto Hawaii, Lono Ono brings you a Hawaiian vacation to your cup!
name: Lolo Ono Hawaiian Shave Ice
